<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idf004b5e0-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9" identifier="/us/usc/t7/s7311"><num value="7311">§ 7311.</num><heading> Establishment</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">There is established a commission to be known as the “Commission on 21st Century Production Agriculture” (in this subchapter referred to as the “Commission”).</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idf004b5e1-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9">(<ref href="/us/pl/104/127/tI/s181">Pub. L. 104–127, title I, § 181</ref>, <date date="1996-04-04">Apr. 4, 1996</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/110/938">110 Stat. 938</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
